{"_id":"MTJiNGJlNTc2MjQ0","name":"Fel'rekt Lafeen","permission":{"default":0},"type":"npc","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":13,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":1,"save":0},"dex":{"value":18,"proficient":1,"min":3,"mod":4,"save":6},"con":{"value":14,"proficient":1,"min":3,"mod":2,"save":4},"int":{"value":11,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0},"wis":{"value":13,"proficient":1,"min":3,"mod":1,"save":3},"cha":{"value":14,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":2,"save":0}},"attributes":{"ac":{"value":"18","min":0,"formula":"studded leather, shield"},"hp":{"value":84,"min":0,"max":84,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"13d8+26"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":4,"prof":0,"total":4},"spellcasting":"cha","speed":{"value":"30 ft","special":""},"prof":2,"spelldc":10,"spellLevel":0,"bar1":{"value":84,"min":0,"max":84},"bar2":{"value":18,"min":0,"max":0}},"details":{"biography":{"value":"\n<hr><section class=\"secret\"><p><strong>GM Notes :</strong> </p><p><span id=\"userscript-docs-internal-guid-5d550360-e43b-5385-738f-5dc547a8c929\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">Firearms aren't widely available in the North, but some members of Bregan D'aerthe are equipped with Lantanese pistols, bullets, and packets of smokepowder. These drow gunslingers are expert pistoleers, as skilled with their guns as the best archers are with their bows.<br></span></span><br><b>Fel'rekt Lafeen </b>is a male drow who was born female. Unhappy with the treatment of males in his society, he petitioned to join Bregan D'aerthe. Jarlaxle took a shine to Fel'rekt almost immediately, and the young drow has since become one of Jarlaxle's most loyal lieutenants. Eager to prove himself, Fel'rekt is quick to volunteer for tasks and hurls himself into combat with verve.<br><br>Fel'rekt and Krebbyg Masq'il'yr are close friends and work as a team, trading banter and jokes at their enemies' expense. Fel'rekt lacks the cruelty common to most drow, and he won't kill an adversary unless he is left with no other choice.