{"_id":"NDFiYWYxYjBjZTQ3","name":"Swarm of Mechanical Spiders","permission":{"default":0},"type":"npc","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":3,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":-4,"save":0},"dex":{"value":13,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":1,"save":0},"con":{"value":10,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0},"int":{"value":1,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":-5,"save":0},"wis":{"value":7,"proficient":1,"min":3,"mod":-2,"save":0},"cha":{"value":1,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":-5,"save":0}},"attributes":{"ac":{"value":"12","min":0,"formula":"natural armor"},"hp":{"value":22,"min":0,"max":22,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"58"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":1,"prof":0,"total":1},"spellcasting":"","speed":{"value":"20 ft","special":"climb 20 ft"},"prof":2,"spelldc":10,"spellLevel":0,"bar1":{"value":22,"min":0,"max":22},"bar2":{"value":12,"min":0,"max":0}},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<h2>The Nature of Swarms</h2>\nThe swarms presented here aren’t ordinary or benign assemblies of little creatures. They form as a result of some sinister or unwholesome influence. A vampire can summon swarms of bats and rats from the darkest corners of the night, while the very presence of a mummy lord can cause scarab beetles to boil up from the sand-filled depths of its tomb. A hag might have the power to turn swarms of ravens against her enemies, while a yuan-ti abomination might have swarms of poisonous snakes slithering in its wake. Even druids can’t charm these swarms, and their aggressiveness is borderline unnatural.<br><br>\n\n<h2>Traits</h2><strong>Swarm</strong>: The swarm can occupy another creature's space and vice versa, and the swarm can move through any opening large enough for a Tiny insect. The swarm can't regain hit points or gain temporary hit points.<br><br><strong>Spider Climb</strong>: The swarm can climb difficult surfaces, including upside down on ceilings, without needing to make an ability check.<br><br><strong>Web Sense</strong>: While in contact with a web, the swarm knows the exact location of any other creature in contact with the same web.<br><br><strong>Web Walker</strong>: The swarm ignores movement restrictions caused by webbing.<br><br>\n\n<h2>Actions</h2>\n\n<strong>Bites (swarm has more than half HP)</strong>: <em>Melee Weapon Attack:</em> +3 to hit, reach 0 ft., one target in the swarm's space. <em>Hit:</em> 10 (4d4) piercing damage.<br><br>\n\n<strong>Bites (swarm has half HP or less)</strong>: <em>Melee Weapon Attack:</em> +3 to hit, reach 0 ft., one target in the swarm's space. <em>Hit:</em> 5 (2d4) piercing damage.\n<hr><section class=\"secret\"><p><strong>GM Notes :</strong> </p><p><span id=\"userscript-docs-internal-guid-9d6aee47-01ff-c42b-902b-ebcd7ce1e325\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">The trunk in area U4 isn't locked. Lifting the lid causes panels in the front and sides to open, releasing a <b>swarm of mechanical spiders </b>that attacks anyone other than Jarlaxle.</span></span><br></p></section>","public":""},"alignment":"Unaligned","race":"","type":"swarm of Tiny constructs","environment":"","cr":0.5,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":100},"source":"Roll 20","class":""},"traits":{"size":"med","di":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":["bludgeoning","piercing","slashing"],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":["lightning"],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":["charmed","frightened","grappled","paralyzed","petrified","poisoned","prone","restrained","stunned"],"custom":""},"senses":"blindsight 10 ft., passive Perception 8","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","bonus":0,"mod":1,"passive":11},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":-2,"passive":8},"arc":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":-5,"passive":5},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","bonus":0,"mod":-4,"passive":6},"dec":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","bonus":0,"mod":-5,"passive":5},"his":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":-5,"passive":5},"ins":{"value":0,"abilit