{"_id":"NDM4ZWJhYzEyZjc5","name":"Rock Gnome Engineer","permission":{"default":0},"type":"npc","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":10,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0},"dex":{"value":10,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0},"con":{"value":10,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0},"int":{"value":14,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":2,"save":0},"wis":{"value":10,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0},"cha":{"value":11,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0}},"attributes":{"ac":{"value":"10","min":0,"formula":""},"hp":{"value":7,"min":0,"max":7,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"2d6"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0},"spellcasting":"int","speed":{"value":"25 ft","special":""},"prof":2,"spelldc":10,"spellLevel":0,"bar1":{"value":7,"min":0,"max":7},"bar2":{"value":10,"min":0,"max":0}},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<div style=\"text-align: left\">Apprentices are novice arcane spellcasters who serve more experienced wizards or attend school. They perform menial work such as cooking and cleaning in exchange for education in the ways of magic.<br></div><br><h2>Variant: Familiars </h2>Any spellcaster that can cast the find familiar spell (such as an apprentice, warlock, or wizard) is likely to have a familiar. The familiar can be one of the creatures described in the spell (see the <em>Player’s Handbook</em>) or some other Tiny monster, such as a cranium rat, a crawling claw, a gazer, an imp, a pseudodragon, or a quasit.<br><br><h2>Traits</h2><strong>Spellcasting</strong>: The apprentice is a 1st-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC 12, +4 to hit with spell attacks). It has the following wizard spells prepared:<br><br>• Cantrips (at will): <em>fire bolt</em>, <em>mending</em>, <em>prestidigitation</em><br>• 1st level (2 slots): <em>burning hands</em>, <em>disguise self</em>, <em>shield</em><br><br><h2>Actions</h2><strong>Fire Bolt</strong>: <em>Ranged Spell Attack:</em> +4 to hit, range 120 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 5 (1d10) fire damage. A flammable object hit by this spell ignites if it isn't being carried or worn.<br><br><strong>Dagger (Melee)</strong>: <em>Melee Weapon Attack:</em> +2 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 2 (1d4) piercing damage.<br><br><strong>Dagger (Ranged)</strong>: <em>Ranged Weapon Attack:</em> +2 to hit, range 20/60 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 2 (1d4) piercing damage.<br>\n<hr><section class=\"secret\"><p><strong>GM Notes :</strong> </p><p><span id=\"userscript-docs-internal-guid-e48bfcb2-e8b1-4a68-6bd7-a199b06d854b\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">Three <b>rock gnome engineers</b> named Lorella Middenpump, Tervaround Waggletop, and Anverth Leffery are on duty in U7b, along with two drow elite warriors named Karabal L'enz and Marro Qaz'arrt. The drow guard the control room and keep the gnomes on task.<br></span></span><br><span id=\"userscript-docs-internal-guid-ce24125d-e8b1-f8ff-9588-f078f9d23585\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">In area U8 each compartment contains an off-duty rock gnome engineer sleeping in a small hammock, beneath which are two steel footlockers. The four rock gnomes are named Cockaby Fapplestamp, Ellywick Fiddlefen, Gerbo Reese, and Zaffrab Horcusporcus.</span></span><br></p></section>","public":""},"alignment":"Neutral Good","race":"","type":"humanoid (rock gnome)","environment":"","cr":0.25,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":50},"source":"Roll 20","class":""},"traits":{"size":"sm","di":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":[],"custom":""},"senses":"darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 10","languages":{"value":["common","gnomish"],"custom":""}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","bonus":0,"mod":0,"passive":10},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":0,"passive":10},"arc":{"value":1,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":4,"passive":14},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","