{"_id":"NTY4ZTRhZjNkYzc1","name":"Fala Lefaliir","permission":{"default":0},"type":"npc","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":10,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0},"dex":{"value":12,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":1,"save":0},"con":{"value":13,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":1,"save":0},"int":{"value":12,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":1,"save":0},"wis":{"value":15,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":2,"save":0},"cha":{"value":11,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0}},"attributes":{"ac":{"value":"11","min":0,"formula":"16 with barkskin"},"hp":{"value":27,"min":0,"max":27,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"5d8 + 5"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":1,"prof":0,"total":1},"spellcasting":"wis","speed":{"value":"30 ft","special":""},"prof":2,"spelldc":10,"spellLevel":0,"bar1":{"value":27,"min":0,"max":27},"bar2":{"value":11,"min":0,"max":0}},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<div style=\"text-align: left\"><strong>Druids</strong> dwell in forests and other secluded  wilderness locations, where they protect the natural  world from monsters and the encroachment of  civilization. Some are <strong>tribal shamans</strong> who heal the  sick, pray to animal spirits, and provide spiritual  guidance.<br></div><br>\n\n<h2>Traits</h2><strong>Spellcasting</strong>: The druid is a 4th-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC 12, +4 to hit with spell attacks). It has the following druid spells prepared: <br><br>• Cantrips (at will): <em>druidcraft, produce flame, shillelagh</em><br>• 1st level (4 slots): <em>entangle, longstrider, speak with animals, thunderwave</em><br>• 2nd level (3 slots): <em>animal messenger, barkskin</em><br><br>\n\n<h2>Actions</h2>\n\n<strong>Quarterstaff (One-Handed)</strong>: <em>Melee Weapon Attack:</em> +2 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 3 (1d6) bludgeoning damage.<br><br>\n\n<strong>Quarterstaff (Two-Handed)</strong>: <em>Melee Weapon Attack:</em> +2 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 4 (1d8) bludgeoning damage.<br><br>\n\n<strong>Quarterstaff (with Shillelagh)</strong>: <em>Melee Weapon Attack:</em> +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 6 (1d8 + 2) bludgeoning damage.<br><br><strong>Produce Flame</strong>: <em>Ranged Spell Attack</em>: +4 to hit, range 30 ft., one creature. <em>Hit</em>: 4 (1d8) fire damage.\n<hr><section class=\"secret\"><p><strong>GM Notes :</strong> </p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\"><b>Fala Lefaliir</b>, an herbalist and a member of the Guild of Apothecaries and Physicians, operates out of this stately, three-story town house, the third floor of which has been converted into a greenhouse. Its translucent glass walls allow anyone on the street to see the rainbow of flowers blossoming within.<br></span><br>Fala Lefaliir is an outgoing wood elf with long, braided hair. Like the elven god Corellon Larethian, Fala is neither male nor female. If referred to as “he” or “she,” Fala gently requests to be addressed by name or as “they.” Fala is friends with a member of the Zhentarim named Ziraj, who saved Fala's life. He visits Fala from time to time, and Fala has set aside a room for him on the second floor.</p></section>","public":""},"alignment":"Chaotic Good","race":"","type":"humanoid (wood elf)","environment":"","cr":2,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":450},"source":"Roll 20","class":""},"traits":{"size":"med","di":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":[],"custom":""},"senses":"darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 14","languages":{"value":["common","druidic","elvish"],"custom":""}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","bonus":0,"mod":1,"passive":11},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":2,"passive":12},"arc":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":1,"passive":11},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","bonus":0,"mod":0,"passive":10},"de