<em>Hit:</em> 5 (1d10) fire damage. A flammable object hit by this spell ignites if it isn't being carried or worn.<br><br><strong>Dagger (Melee)</strong>: <em>Melee Weapon Attack:</em> +2 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 2 (1d4) piercing damage.<br><br><strong>Dagger (Ranged)</strong>: <em>Ranged Weapon Attack:</em> +2 to hit, range 20/60 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 2 (1d4) piercing damage.<br>\n<hr><section class=\"secret\"><p><strong>GM Notes :</strong> </p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">Five bald shield dwarves, their heads covered with purple eye tattoos, sit around the edge of a glowing circle on the floor. Their eyes are scrunched shut, but they are aware of their surroundings.<br><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">Protruding from the ceiling, directly above the circle, is a large, flaring bronze “bell” similar in shape to the mouth of a tuba.<br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\"><br>The five tattooed dwarves operate Xanathar's “panopticus” magical surveillance system. They fight only in self-defense.&nbsp;</span><span>Nihiloor the mind flayer has psychically and surgically altered the dwarves so that they sleep with one eye open and half their brains asleep at any time.&nbsp;</span></p></section>","public":""},"alignment":"Neutral","race":"","type":"humanoid (shield dwarf)","environment":"","cr":0.25,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":50},"source":"Roll 20","class":""},"traits":{"size":"med","di":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":[],"custom":""},"senses":"darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 10","languages":{"value":["common","dwarvish"],"custom":""}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"c