{"_id":"YWRlYjJiZTUyZTBh","name":"Flying Snake","permission":{"default":0},"type":"npc","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":4,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":-3,"save":0},"dex":{"value":18,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":4,"save":0},"con":{"value":11,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0},"int":{"value":2,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":-4,"save":0},"wis":{"value":12,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":1,"save":0},"cha":{"value":5,"proficient":0,"min":3,"mod":-3,"save":0}},"attributes":{"ac":{"value":"14","min":0,"formula":""},"hp":{"value":5,"min":0,"max":5,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"2d4"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":4,"prof":0,"total":4},"spellcasting":"","speed":{"value":"30 ft","special":"fly 60 ft, swim 30 ft"},"prof":2,"spelldc":10,"spellLevel":0,"bar1":{"value":5,"min":0,"max":5},"bar2":{"value":14,"min":0,"max":0}},"details":{"biography":{"value":"Picture: <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=JournalEntry data-id=ZjA1MzcwMjRmYWQ1 ><i class=\"fas fa-book-open\"></i>Handout: Flying Snake</a><br><br>A <strong>flying snake</strong> is a brightly colored, winged serpent found in remote jungles. Tribespeople and cultists sometimes domesticate flying snakes to serve as messengers that deliver scrolls wrapped in their coils.<br><br>\n<h2>Traits</h2><strong>Flyby</strong>: The snake doesn't provoke opportunity attacks when it flies out of an enemy's reach.<br><br><h2>Actions</h2><strong>Bite</strong>: <em>Melee Weapon Attack:</em> +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. <em>Hit:</em> 1 (1d1) piercing damage plus 7 (3d4) poison damage.\n<hr><section class=\"secret\"><p><strong>GM Notes :</strong> </p><p><span id=\"userscript-docs-internal-guid-5608aee5-fd95-c155-1062-ccd18c04c9d3\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">Davil offers membership in the Zhentarim to interested characters, then assigns them their first mission. Subsequent mission briefings are written on scrolls and delivered by<b> flying snakes</b>.</span></span></p><hr><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">A spectator floats in the middle of the area K22, and four<b> flying snakes</b> flutter above the rafters.</span></p><hr><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\"><span id=\"userscript-docs-internal-guid-375bb113-fd97-056f-8bc5-690bca4c5a5a\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">Urstul is a large, heavyset man in his forties. He storms about House Gralhund like he owns the place. He has a collection of black<b> flying snakes </b>that he uses as couriers to deliver messages to underlings throughout the city.</span></span><br></span></p></section>","public":""},"alignment":"Unaligned","race":"","type":"beast","environment":"","cr":0.125,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":25},"source":"Roll 20","class":""},"traits":{"size":"tiny","di":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":[],"custom":""},"senses":"blindsight 10 ft., passive Perception 11","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","bonus":0,"mod":4,"passive":14},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":1,"passive":11},"arc":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":-4,"passive":6},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","bonus":0,"mod":-3,"passive":7},"dec":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","bonus":0,"mod":-3,"passive":7},"his":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":-4,"passive":6},"ins":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":1,"passive":11},"itm":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","bonus":0,"mod":-3,"passive":7},"inv":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":-4,"passive":6},"med":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":1,"passive":11},"nat":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":-4,"passive":6},"prc":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":1,"passive":11},"prf":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","bonus":0,"mod":-3,